Package: bayesm.HART
Title: Bayesian Multinomial Logit Models with HART Priors
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Wiemann", , "wiemann@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Metropolis-withing-Gibbs sampler for the Bayesian 
  hierarchical multinomial logit model with HART priors developed in Wiemann 
  (2025). Originally a fork of the bayesm and BART R packages.
